### Directly Embedding Custom Component in Recharts v3.0

Source: https://github.com/recharts/recharts/wiki/3.0-migration-guide

This example highlights the new flexibility in Recharts v3.0, allowing direct embedding of `MyCustomComponent` within a `BarChart`. This approach renders the custom component directly, eliminating the need for the `Customized` wrapper. It simplifies the component structure and improves readability for custom chart elements.

```jsx
<BarChart width={1100} height={250} data={data}>
  <MyCustomComponent />
</BarChart>
```
